## Listing Process

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant U as VIVIM User
    participant V as Vault
    participant M as Marketplace
    participant C as Blockchain
    
    U->>V: Select ACUs for listing
    V->>V: Generate Merkle root of selection
    
    V->>V: Create ZK proof of properties
    Note over V: - Count verification<br/>- Date range verification<br/>- Topic distribution
    
    V->>M: Submit listing
    M->>C: Publish listing descriptor
    M->>U: Listing active
    
    Note over C: On-chain:<br/>- Merkle root<br/>- Price<br/>- Terms<br/>- Seller DID
```

## Purchase and Delivery Flow

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant B as Buyer
    participant M as Marketplace
    participant S as Seller Vault
    participant C as Blockchain
    
    B->>M: Select listing
    B->>B: Generate ephemeral key pair
    
    B->>M: Submit purchase + payment + pubkey
    M->>C: Lock payment in escrow
    
    M->>S: Purchase notification
    S->>S: Verify on-chain transaction
    S->>S: Verify consent permits sale
    S->>S: Derive delivery key (ECDH)
    S->>S: Re-encrypt selected ACUs
    
    S->>M: Deliver encrypted vesicles
    S->>M: Delivery proof
    
    M->>B: Deliver vesicles
    B->>B: Decrypt with ephemeral key
    
    B->>M: Confirm receipt
    M->>C: Release escrow to seller
    M->>C: Record access grant
    
    Note over C: Buyer now has<br/>capability token<br/>for listed data
```

## ZK Proof Architecture

```mermaid
flowchart TB
    subgraph "Zero-Knowledge Proofs"
        
        subgraph "Ownership Proof"
            OP1[Public: VaultRoot, ACU_id]
            OP2[Private: Merkle Path, sk]
            OP1 --> OP3[Prove: I own this ACU]
        end
        
        subgraph "Consent Validity"
            CP1[Public: ConsentRoot, buyer, action]
            CP2[Private: Consent, Merkle Path]
            CP1 --> CP3[Prove: Valid consent exists]
        end
        
        subgraph "Data Property Attestation"
            PP1[Public: DataCommit, properties]
            PP2[Private: ACU set]
            PP1 --> PP3[Prove: Data has properties]
        end
        
        subgraph "Aggregate Statistics"
            AP1[Public: DataCommit, statistic]
            AP2[Private: ACU set]
            AP1 --> AP3[Prove: Statistic is true]
        end
        
        OP3 --> Verify[ZKP Verification]
        CP3 --> Verify
        PP3 --> Verify
        AP3 --> Verify
    end
    
    style OP3 fill:#e94560,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style CP3 fill:#3498db,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style PP3 fill:#27ae60,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style AP3 fill:#9b59b6,stroke:#333,color:#fff
```

## Minimum Disclosure Review Packet

```mermaid
flowchart TB
    subgraph "MDRP: Minimum Disclosure Review Packet"
        Full[Full ACU Content] --> Extract[Extract Features]
        
        Extract --> Optimize[Information Bottleneck]
        
        Optimize -->|Minimize| Disclosure[I(M; R)]
        Optimize -->|Maintain| Decision[I(R; D) ≥ τ]
        
        Disclosure --> Packet[Review Packet R]
        Decision --> Packet
        
        Packet --> Review[Third Party Review]
        Review --> Approve[Approve / Deny]
    end
    
    note over Optimize: optimize: min I(M;R)<br/>subject to: I(R;D) ≥ τ<br/><br/>M = memory object<br/>R = review packet<br/>D = decision
    
    style Optimize fill:#e94560,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style Packet fill:#0f3460,stroke:#333,color:#fff
```

